title: The Indochina, Vietnam and Korea Wars - Collection 4
description:
The Indochina, Vietnam and Korea Wars - Collection 4:

-  Ca & Dror - Morning Headband for Hue; an Account of the Battle for Hue, Vietnam 1968 (2014)

-  Chomsky - Rethinking Camelot; JFK, the Vietnam War, and US Political Culture (1993)
